    <title>Angular 04- 資料繫結方法(三) - 事件繫結(Event Binding)</title>
    <url>/2021/06/13/Angular/Angular-note-04/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a><strong>基本概念</strong></h2><ul>
<li><p>語法： <code>(event) = &quot;handler&quot;</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>概念：單向繫結，由template(html)透過瀏覽器事件觸發後，去呼叫component(ts)上的方法。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="運用"><a href="#運用" class="headerlink" title="運用"></a><strong>運用</strong></h2><p><strong>HTML</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>方法一：onclick 中間加入 <code>-</code><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img on-click=<span class="string">&quot;changeTitle()&quot;</span> [title]=<span class="string">&quot;title&quot;</span> [src]=<span class="string">&quot;imgurl&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>方法二：onclick 改成 <code>(click)</code> (建議用法)<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img (click)=<span class="string">&quot;changeTitle()&quot;</span> [title]=<span class="string">&quot;title&quot;</span> [src]=<span class="string">&quot;imgurl&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>TS</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; Component &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;@angular/core&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;app-root&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">templateUrl</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.html&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">styleUrls</span>: [<span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.scss&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">AppComponent</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  title = <span class="string">&#x27;前端小白&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  url = <span class="string">&#x27;www.google.com&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  imgurl = <span class="string">&#x27;/assets/images/logo.png&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">constructor</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">changeTitle</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="built_in">this</span>.title = <span class="string">&quot;Google&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="使用-event參數-取得MouseEvent的詳細資訊"><a href="#使用-event參數-取得MouseEvent的詳細資訊" class="headerlink" title="使用$event參數-取得MouseEvent的詳細資訊"></a><strong>使用$event參數-取得MouseEvent的詳細資訊</strong></h2><p>可注意資訊：<code>$event.target</code> 為點擊下去的DOM物件</p>
<p><strong>HTML</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img (click)=<span class="string">&quot;changeTitle($event)&quot;</span> [title]=<span class="string">&quot;title&quot;</span> [src]=<span class="string">&quot;imgurl&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>TS</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; Component &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;@angular/core&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;app-root&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">templateUrl</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.html&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">styleUrls</span>: [<span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.scss&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">AppComponent</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  title = <span class="string">&#x27;前端小白&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  url = <span class="string">&#x27;www.google.com&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  imgurl = <span class="string">&#x27;/assets/images/logo.png&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">constructor</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">changeTitle</span>(<span class="params">$event: <span class="built_in">any</span></span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.title = <span class="string">&quot;Google&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log($event);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="練習：按altKey後點擊滑鼠改變title有兩種寫法"><a href="#練習：按altKey後點擊滑鼠改變title有兩種寫法" class="headerlink" title="練習：按altKey後點擊滑鼠改變title有兩種寫法"></a><strong>練習：按altKey後點擊滑鼠改變title有兩種寫法</strong></h2><p><strong>寫法一</strong></p>
<p><strong>HTML</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img (click)=<span class="string">&quot;changeTitle($event)&quot;</span> [title]=<span class="string">&quot;title&quot;</span> [src]=<span class="string">&quot;imgurl&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>TS</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; Component &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;@angular/core&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;app-root&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">templateUrl</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.html&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">styleUrls</span>: [<span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.scss&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">AppComponent</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  title = <span class="string">&#x27;前端小白&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  url = <span class="string">&#x27;www.google.com&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  imgurl = <span class="string">&#x27;/assets/images/logo.png&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">constructor</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">changeTitle</span>(<span class="params">$event: MouseEvent</span>)</span> &#123; <span class="comment">// 先輸入MouseEvent</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> ($event.altKey) &#123;            <span class="comment">// 可以在此直接選取altKey</span></span><br><span class="line">       title = <span class="string">&quot;Google&quot;</span>;            <span class="comment">// 較不易打錯字</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">console</span>.log($event);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>寫法二(較簡潔)</strong><br><strong>HTML</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img (click)=<span class="string">&quot;changeTitle($event.altKey)&quot;</span> [title]=<span class="string">&quot;title&quot;</span> [src]=<span class="string">&quot;imgurl&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>TS</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; Component &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;@angular/core&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;app-root&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">templateUrl</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.html&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">styleUrls</span>: [<span class="string">&#x27;./app.component.scss&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">AppComponent</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  title = <span class="string">&#x27;前端小白&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  url = <span class="string">&#x27;www.google.com&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  imgurl = <span class="string">&#x27;/assets/images/logo.png&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">constructor</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">changeTitle</span>(<span class="params">altKey: <span class="built_in">boolean</span></span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (altKey) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">this</span>.title = <span class="string">&quot;Google&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
